name: Protox-1
overview: A game created by Giuseppe Vollara aka VG Vox ak Pinov Vox for the 2019 SEUCK Compo. It is the Year 2325 ... The protagonist Captain John Rostar catapulted into a parallel universe in a hostile world dominated by technology and strange aliens and giant animals that resemble giant reptiles. The Captain must command a fleet of spacecraft and defeat and rescue two important Androids to leave this parallel universe. Find the 2 friends of your friends and defeat the aliens and monsters of the PROTOX1 planet.
